{
  "stem": "10406.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the Germans, instead of giving people orders individually, they would-- they would tell the-- judenrat was they would come in maybe to the rabbi and say, by tomorrow 12:00, I want to have so many people forming a judenrat or a committee that will represent the Jews, and if not, you'll be shot.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was not-- most of the time and in most cases, it was not a glorious job that everybody ran to grab, although there were some abuses, maybe, in other towns, you know, that I read about or hear about.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But most people did not want to be involved in that because if something happened and the judenrat rather tried to represent the Jews, and let's say protested, so they took them and shot them and they-- they said, form another one.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So but now, the judenrat would order-- let's say the Germans wanted 50 people, 100 people to do work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would have to provide them, and that was on a daily basis.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, they would also-- the Germans would also go, suddenly appear in town, and-- and whoever was Jewish-- and, of course, the Jews had to wear bands.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Do you remember getting a band?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't have to wear it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother and sister already wore it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it's interesting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have running water in our house, but there was a pump about a block away, so we had to go to get water.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we already knew the fear was there that you can be captured any time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So being that they were wearing-- we had two kinds of situations.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The white bands were the star of David, and they also made us wear yellow circles in the front and in the back.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
